caption.p: Analysis of unique differential metabolites in SASCs, EASCs, and PASCs. (A) A Wayne chart of differential metabolites between SASCs vs. EASCs with SASCs vs. PASCs. (B) Analysis of metabolic pathways of unique differential metabolites between SASCs and EASCs. (C) Overview of the enrichment of unique differential metabolites between SASCs and EASCs. (D) Analysis of metabolic pathways of unique differential metabolites between SASCs and PASCs. (E) Overview of the enrichment of unique differential metabolites between SASCs and PASCs.
